[106415481440557230121,100769939815488657532,One of my favorite places in Westchester. They take their beer and their food seriously, always something new and notable on tap. The food is creative, fresh and well prepared high end pub food. This is what a grown up pub is supposed to be like: great food, great beer and great service. Be warned, something this good gets crowded fast so arrive early or relax with a beer at the bar and settle in.]
